Titolo: Café 0: The Drowned Mermaid

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: Café 0: The Drowned Mermaid (カフェ・ゼロ～溺れた人魚～, Kafe zero ~ oboreta ningyo ~) is a mystery visual novel video game developed and released by ROSEVERTE for Windows and Mac OS on October 4, 2011. Originally released in English, the game was later officially translated into Japanese and German. On April 22, 2012 the game was released on Desura and a version for Android followed on March 8, 2013. The Japanese and the English version were released for iOS on September 27, 2012.